        h5 Secondary
        p You can add another class #[code label-secondary], #[code label-secondary-dark], #[code label-secondary-light] for labels colored with secondary colors.
        span.label.label-secondary.mr-1 secondary label
        span.label.label-secondary-dark.mr-1 secondary label dark
        span.label.label-secondary-light.mr-1 secondary label light
        pre.code(data-lang='HTML')
