        h5 Control
        p You can add another class #[code label-disabled], #[code label-error], #[code label-info], #[code label-success] and #[code label-warning] for colored labels.
        span.label.label-disabled.mr-1 disabled label
        span.label.label-error.mr-1 error label
        span.label.label-info.mr-1 info label
        span.label.label-success.mr-1 success label
        span.label.label-warning.mr-1 warning label
        pre.code(data-lang='HTML')
